WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 18=

00:00:06.300 --> 00:00:07.140
Suisui!

00:00:16.780 --> 00:00:17.940
Xiao Heng.

00:00:17.980 --> 00:00:20.300
This formation was set up just for you.

00:00:20.580 --> 00:00:21.780
You won't escape.

00:00:22.180 --> 00:00:23.140
Get him!

00:00:27.380 --> 00:00:28.500
Father!

00:00:28.580 --> 00:00:30.779
Don't be scared. I'm here to save you.

00:00:30.780 --> 00:00:31.780
Suisui.

00:00:45.980 --> 00:00:46.979
My formation!

00:00:46.980 --> 00:00:47.939
How infuriating!

00:00:47.940 --> 00:00:49.500
Kill him!

00:00:49.580 --> 00:00:50.820
In your dreams!

00:01:21.820 --> 00:01:25.140
This little money isn't even enough
to cover my travel expenses.

00:01:28.900 --> 00:01:30.340
Bad Crown Prince.

00:01:30.380 --> 00:01:32.060
Xiao Jing.

00:01:55.820 --> 00:01:59.420
You again. It's always you!

00:01:59.460 --> 00:02:02.060
My carefully planned scheme

00:02:04.420 --> 00:02:07.540
has been ruined by that girl again.

00:02:11.660 --> 00:02:13.539
I want...

00:02:13.540 --> 00:02:15.259
I want to kill...

00:02:15.260 --> 00:02:17.140
Kill...

00:02:29.220 --> 00:02:31.580
Why am I here?

00:02:32.900 --> 00:02:35.339
Xiao Heng, what are you trying to do?

00:02:35.340 --> 00:02:36.619
I am the Crown Prince.

00:02:36.620 --> 00:02:38.099
Are you going to lay a hand on me?

00:02:38.100 --> 00:02:39.220
Crown Prince?

00:02:40.160 --> 00:02:42.680
Setting up a formation to assassinate
a royal prince of the court.

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:44.220
Surely Your Highness knows

00:02:44.340 --> 00:02:46.420
what crime that is?

00:02:46.700 --> 00:02:48.819
You... What are you talking about?

00:02:48.820 --> 00:02:50.660
I... I don't understand.

00:03:05.700 --> 00:03:06.580
Father.

00:03:06.740 --> 00:03:08.299
He's not pretending.

00:03:08.300 --> 00:03:09.860
He was being controlled.

00:03:10.180 --> 00:03:11.300
Crow.

00:03:14.100 --> 00:03:16.820
Smell him and see if this is the scent
of the Imperial Preceptor's Manor.

00:03:17.700 --> 00:03:18.420
Mm.

00:03:18.700 --> 00:03:19.499
It's him.

00:03:19.500 --> 00:03:20.699
That's the Taoist's scent.

00:03:20.700 --> 00:03:22.899
Even if he were burned to ashes,
I'd still recognize it.

00:03:22.900 --> 00:03:25.300
That pigeon from last time
had the same smell.

00:03:26.740 --> 00:03:28.940
So it really
was that Taoist behind this.

00:03:30.180 --> 00:03:31.820
Even if he was being controlled,

00:03:31.980 --> 00:03:33.540
he's still a pawn.

00:03:33.740 --> 00:03:35.820
Even if I spare him today,

00:03:35.900 --> 00:03:37.419
he'll still be used again tomorrow.

00:03:37.420 --> 00:03:39.060
Uncle, please don't!

00:03:43.300 --> 00:03:44.699
Uncle.

00:03:44.700 --> 00:03:46.499
Please spare him, Uncle.

00:03:46.500 --> 00:03:49.939
For the sake of me secretly warning you.

00:03:49.940 --> 00:03:51.020
What?

00:03:51.340 --> 00:03:52.860
Rui'er, you...

00:03:53.660 --> 00:03:56.139
Father, Xiao Rui came to warn us.

00:03:56.140 --> 00:03:57.219
If it weren't for him,

00:03:57.220 --> 00:03:59.039
I wouldn't have known

00:03:59.040 --> 00:04:00.620
you were in danger at Luoyan Slope.

00:04:05.140 --> 00:04:06.219
Get up.

00:04:06.220 --> 00:04:08.220
Thank you, Uncle.

00:04:10.020 --> 00:04:11.699
Uncle.

00:04:11.700 --> 00:04:13.780
You may escape death,

00:04:13.820 --> 00:04:15.780
but you won't escape punishment.

00:04:16.820 --> 00:04:18.979
What... What punishment?

00:04:18.980 --> 00:04:21.699
Rescue fee,
emotional distress fee, travel expenses,

00:04:21.700 --> 00:04:24.579
lost work compensation, suona
depreciation fee, crow overtime fee,

00:04:24.580 --> 00:04:26.019
and puppy patrol fee.

00:04:26.020 --> 00:04:29.699
Seven charges in total.
One hundred thousand taels of gold.

00:04:29.700 --> 00:04:30.739
What?

00:04:30.740 --> 00:04:31.339
You...

00:04:31.340 --> 00:04:34.020
If you don't want to pay,
that's fine too.

00:04:34.140 --> 00:04:35.179
In that case,

00:04:35.180 --> 00:04:37.979
I'll bring this puppet talisman

00:04:37.980 --> 00:04:39.979
straight to Grandfather.

00:04:39.980 --> 00:04:44.699
Then I'll tell him that Uncle
colluded with the Imperial Preceptor

00:04:44.700 --> 00:04:46.220
to murder a royal prince.

00:04:46.500 --> 00:04:47.819
By then,

00:04:47.820 --> 00:04:49.159
if Grandfather

00:04:49.160 --> 00:04:52.260
personally questions you,

00:04:52.420 --> 00:04:55.139
will you confess,

00:04:55.140 --> 00:04:57.460
or not?

00:04:57.700 --> 00:04:58.820
You...

00:05:06.440 --> 00:05:09.759
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:09.760 --> 00:05:13.599
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:17.119
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:20.080
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:20.960 --> 00:05:24.599
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:24.600 --> 00:05:28.360
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:28.440 --> 00:05:31.759
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:31.760 --> 00:05:35.800
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:45.079
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:45.080 --> 00:05:48.719
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:52.439
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:52.440 --> 00:05:56.079
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:59.759
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:05:59.760 --> 00:06:01.679
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:07.880
♪Good fortune♪